<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12207j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12207j">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12207j"> 207(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> I was just asleep</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Celui-ci se frotta vigoureusement et dit: &ldquo;J&apos;ai failli dormir.&rdquo; <br><font color="green">[The other one rubbed himself vigorously and said: &ldquo;I almost slept.&rdquo;]</font> <small> Maurice Delafosse, <a name="LNEG" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#LNEG"><cite title="source">L'&acirc;me n&egrave;gre</cite></a> (1922) 168 (from the story <i>Farces</i>, about two men who are addicted to sleep, the first one waking only when he is freed from the belly of a python that was eaten by a crocodile that was eaten by a mythical &lsquo;water leopard&rsquo;)</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
